    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your body reacts to the presence of magic. You can cast the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.matSplDetectMagi]{Detect Magic} spell without using a spell slot or components. Constitution is your spellcasting ability for this spell. You faintly glow a color corresponding to the school of magic you detect (you choose the colors).</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Proficiency modifier. You regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest.</p><section id=\"secret-ps7IbUV9MahRRs76\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>When you reach this level, you will have the Detect Magic spell automatically added to your Spells tab with the appropriate number of uses per long rest.</p></section>",
